 Of course, it is a bit of luck to find furniture that makes strip lights. 

00:05:11.096 --> 00:05:14.057
 But, hey, how can you live without luck? 

00:05:14.057 --> 00:05:18.482
 I hope that you will have a little luck in finding the right tools. 

00:05:18.482 --> 00:05:21.534
 I also hope that you find this video inspiring. 

